    "data": [
        {
            "title": "馬斯克阿媽上海買金 身兼多職媲美首富阿仔",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"首富馬斯克阿媽Maye Musk近日發布上海買金短片，再次掀起話題。\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"732\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.OWbSQZ64dQ08MUTusggIg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTczMg--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-02/b71b5480-0e20-11f1-b5af-ef64e1ce19df\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">首富馬斯克阿媽<span>Maye Musk</span>近日發布上海買金短片，再次掀起話題。</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">馬斯克係首富亦是超級KOL，佢阿媽原來都係時裝界網紅，獨力培育一門三傑的她，現時身兼模特兒、時裝品牌代言、KOL及營養師多職，對工作熱情不下於首富阿仔。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link rapid-with-clickid etailiffa-link athena-button\" data-i13n=\"sec:shop-now;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Yahoo;elmt:other;pdid:\" data-ylk=\"slk:下載Yahoo財經APP;sec:shop-now;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Yahoo;elmt:other;pdid:;itc:0\" href=\"https://yhoo.it/3GLNxtA\" rel=\"sponsored\" target=\"_blank\">下載Yahoo財經APP</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>美股外幣即時報價 多國新聞任睇</strong></p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">現身上海買金掀話題 67歲行Catwalk</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">馬斯克阿媽Maye Musk同樣係傳奇人物，她年僅15歲就成為模特兒，早年離婚後帶著三名子搬到多倫多，曾經連交租都成問題，為賺錢要身兼五職，同時以無比毅力完成營養學碩士課程。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5173ce26-83db-4c3a-92c9-2e39afcf3d92-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Maye Musk三名子女，除了大家熟悉的首富馬斯克Elon Musk，二仔Kimbal Musk曾將生意賣盤賺過億美元，及後經營餐飲生意，細女Tosca Musk是知名電影人，擁有資產逾億製作公司，可謂一門三傑。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><blockquote class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull\" style=\"padding-bottom:min(300px, undefined%)\"></div></blockquote><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Maye Musk的傳奇經歷，令她成為全球知名的KOL，她在內地都人氣高企，以往在內地訪問都掀起熱潮。日前她在<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:IG發布短片;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/reels/DUYNn_XkYAm/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">IG發布短片</a>，分享她在上海老舖黃金購買金飾，並對金飾手工讚不絕口，稱希望老舖黃金能夠在紐約開分店，再次成為話題。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"本身是大忙人的Maye Musk，難得與首富阿仔馬斯克同框。(Photo by Jabin Botsford/The Washington Post via Getty Images)\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_yVaKFoN2tDgwA1EY_IVtQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-02/1a453990-0e21-11f1-9bf7-8d05443bf554\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">本身是大忙人的Maye Musk，難得與首富阿仔馬斯克同框。(Photo by Jabin Botsford/The Washington Post via Getty Images)</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">年屆77歲的Maye Musk，為人津津樂道是她並不怕老。她60歲時厭倦了自己的金髮，順其自然地展示自己的白髮，結果白短髮成為她的標記。她到紐約擔任銀髮模特兒，並在67歲時在紐約時裝周行Catwalk，到69歲時擊敗過百位競爭對手，成為CoverGirl最高齡代言人，71歲時推出自傳《A Women Makes A Plan》，這十年間她身體力行地證明甚麼是永不言休。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">兒子是世界首富，理論上Maye Musk做甚麼事都手到拿來。不過事實上馬斯克成為首富後，對Maye Musk最大助力是首富名氣，Maye Musk不少工作都是靠自己的實力取得成功。Maye Musk能夠身兼多職，似乎是受她的父親影響。她回憶童年時父親會帶著子女穿越沙漠旅行，父親的家訓是「活得危險，但要小心」。馬斯克喜歡不斷擴張新業務，由電動車、火箭、機械人到AI，都是以急速步伐搶佔先機，或許都是受「活得危險，但要小心」這個家訓所影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">大家未必有Maye Musk的傳奇人生，不過從她身上，都可以學到掌握多幾門技能，像她所言別讓年齡拖累自己，「越努力、越幸運」。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%AC%E6%96%AF%E5%85%8B%E9%98%BF%E5%AA%BD%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E8%B2%B7%E9%87%91-%E8%BA%AB%E5%85%BC%E5%A4%9A%E8%81%B7%E5%AA%B2%E7%BE%8E%E9%A6%96%E5%AF%8C%E9%98%BF%E4%BB%94-060531499.html",
